<div class=3D"mf-section-0" id=3D"mf-section-0">
<p>Most bowling alleys score your game automatically, but understanding how=
 to score bowling gives you valuable insight to the game and comes in handy=
 if electronic scoring isn=E2=80=99t available. We=E2=80=99ll get you start=
ed by familiarizing you with the layout of the scorecard. Then, we=E2=80=99=
ll show you how to score each turn, including strikes, spares, and open fra=
mes, and how to tally your final score to see how you stack up against othe=
r players.
</p>
