com/Score-Bowling#_note-12">[12]</a>
</sup> Find the number of points you scored in your 10th frame, then add th=
em to your total from the 9th frame to find your final score. For example, =
if your 10th-frame score is 110 and your friend's is 100, you've won the ga=
me. Congratulations!
